'''Chemnitz dialect''' is a distinct [[German language|German]] [[dialect]] of the city of [[Chemnitz]] and an urban variety of [[Vorerzgebirgisch]], a variant of [[Upper Saxon German]].{{sfnp|Khan|Weise|2013|p=231}}

